text: Dokuz Dağın Efesi, or Dokuz Dağın Efesi: Çakici Geliyor is a 1958 Turkish drama film directed by Metin Erksan. It stars Fikret Hakan, Serpil Gül, and Hayri Esen. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1958 films Category:Turkish films Category:Turkish drama films Category:1958 drama films Category:Films directed by Metin Erksan
